# Firebase (client) — realestatebuddy2
# CRITICAL: VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY must be ONLY the key (e.g. AIzaSyCqGecJnmzNf48U0Bt74maxzmdkE-TdtjYey).
# No "key=", no "your-key", no quotes, no pasting twice. One line, 39 characters.
# Firebase Console → Project settings → Your apps → Web app → copy "API key" field only.
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=

# LLM for CSV column mapping (server only) — copy to .env in project root when running server
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=     # or OPENAI_API_KEY= if using OpenAI
